  "original_title": "Significant fall in tea production",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Significant fall in tea production",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka tea production for the month of June 2022 totaled 20.15 M/Kgs, showing a decrease of 5.92 M/Kgs vis-\u00e0-vis 26.07 M/Kgs of June 2021.All elevations have shown a decline over the corresponding month of 2021. When compared with the 27.36 M/Kgs of June 2020, June 2022 shows a decrease of 7.21 M/Kgs. Meanwhile, the first half of 2022 (January-June) cumulative production totalled 132.92 M/Kgs, recording a significant decrease of 28.79 M/Kgs vis-\u00e0-vis 161.71 M/Kgs of January-June 2021.",
        "A pro-level gaming experience with ViewSonic\u2019s latest 240Hz gaming monitor",
        "Hayleys Solar introduces \u2018PV-DG\u2019 solution to help businesses with solar rooftops to optimise fuel usage and reduce costs",
